dct_title_s: Map of Rotorua and environs / published by the Department of Lands and Survey, N.Z., under the authority of R.P. Gough, Surveyor General
dct_description_sm: Map shows: city boundaries, house numbers, 3 classes of roads, and built-up areas. Includes index. Inset: Rotorua city centre. Scale 1:6,250.
dct_creator_sm: New Zealand. Department of Lands and Survey
dct_publisher_sm: Wellington, N.Z. : Department of Lands and Survey, N.Z., 1963.
